#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/home/index.rst:2
msgid "主页"
msgstr "Home"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/home/index.rst:4
msgid "**此页面的用途**"
msgstr "**What this page covers**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/home/index.rst:6
msgid "登录后进入 **主页**，这是系统的入口，集中提供三大功能入口、传送带状态、最近检测任务与产品（PCBA）管理。"
msgstr ""
"After login, you land on the **Home** page — the system's entry point that "
"brings together the three main actions, conveyor status, the recent "
"inspection task list, and product (PCBA) management."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/home/index.rst:-1
msgid "主页概览"
msgstr "Home page overview"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/home/index.rst:12
msgid "**如何进入**"
msgstr "**How to open it**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/home/index.rst:14
msgid "登录系统后自动跳转至主页；在任意页面点击顶部导航栏的系统 Logo 或导航回首页也可返回此页面。"
msgstr ""
"You're routed to Home automatically after login; click the system logo in "
"the top nav bar from any page to come back."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/home/index.rst:18
msgid "**操作流程**"
msgstr "**Workflow**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/home/index.rst:20
msgid "**功能入口**"
msgstr "**Action cards**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/home/index.rst:22
msgid "页面顶部为三个主要入口卡片（管理员/编程员角色可见全部三项；操作员仅可见第一项）："
msgstr ""
"Three primary action cards sit at the top of the page (Administrators and "
"Programmers see all three; Operators see only the first):"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/home/index.rst:24
msgid "**新建检测任务**：选择一个 PCBA 开始检测（详见 :ref:`检测与反馈`）。"
msgstr ""
"**New Inspection Task**: pick a PCBA and start an inspection (see "
":ref:`检测与反馈` for details)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/home/index.rst:25
msgid "**训练PCBA**：注册新的 PCBA / 产品并进入自动编程向导（仅管理员/编程员；详见 :ref:`创建产品`）。"
msgstr ""
"**Train PCBA**: register a new PCBA / product and open the Auto-Programming "
"wizard (Administrators and Programmers only; see :ref:`创建产品`)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/home/index.rst:26
msgid "**工作列表**：查看过去的检测记录与数据分析报告（详见 :ref:`查看检测历史（数据分析报告）`）。"
msgstr ""
"**Worklist**: review past inspection records and the data-analysis report "
"(see :ref:`查看检测历史（数据分析报告）`)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/home/index.rst:28
msgid "**传送带状态**"
msgstr "**Conveyor status**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/home/index.rst:30
msgid ""
"**传送带状态** 区域显示每条传送带（如 Conveyor #A）的实时状态：**空闲**、**运行检测任务中** 或 "
"**定义PCB中**。常用操作："
msgstr ""
"The **Conveyor Status** panel shows the live state of every conveyor (for "
"example, Conveyor #A): **Idle**, **Running inspection**, or **Defining "
"PCB**. Common actions:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/home/index.rst:32
msgid "**重置轨道**：复位传送带 / 清除当前占用。仅在传送带急停（Emergency Stop）激活时生效；当出现异常占用或需要中断时使用。"
msgstr ""
"**Reset Track**: reset the conveyor and clear its current ownership. "
"Effective only when Emergency Stop is active; use it when the conveyor is "
"stuck in an unexpected state."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/home/index.rst:33
msgid "**刷新传送带状态**：手动刷新各传送带的最新状态。"
msgstr "**Refresh Conveyor Status**: manually re-poll every conveyor's state."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/home/index.rst:35
msgid "**最近的检测任务**"
msgstr "**Recent inspection tasks**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/home/index.rst:37
msgid ""
"**最近的检测任务** "
"列表列出最近执行的检测任务，包含以下列：任务（产品名称）、总产品数、合格率、开始时间。点击任意行可进入对应记录，便于快速回看近期生产情况。"
msgstr ""
"The **Recent inspection tasks** list shows recently-run inspections with the"
" columns Task (product name), Total products, Pass rate, and Start time. "
"Click any row to open the corresponding record for a quick look back at "
"recent production."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/home/index.rst:39
msgid "**产品（PCBA）管理**"
msgstr "**Product (PCBA) management**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/home/index.rst:41
msgid ""
"右侧 **管理PCBA** 列表展示所有已创建的产品，包含 PCBA类型、创建时间、最后更新等列。产品名称列同时显示该产品已附加的标签（Tag）。"
msgstr ""
"The **Manage PCBA** list on the right shows every product with columns for "
"PCBA type, Created at, Last updated, and so on. The product-name column also"
" displays the product's tags."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/home/index.rst:43
msgid "每行提供以下操作："
msgstr "Each row offers:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/home/index.rst:45
msgid "**编辑**：进入该产品的编程页面（标记对齐、模板编辑器、拼板、整板检测等）。"
msgstr ""
"**Edit**: open the product's programming page (Mark Alignment, Template "
"Editor, PCB Array, Whole Board Inspection, and so on)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/home/index.rst:46
msgid "**复制**：基于现有产品创建一个副本。"
msgstr "**Duplicate**: create a copy of an existing product."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/home/index.rst:47
msgid "**删除**：删除该产品及其数据（需在弹出确认框中确认）。"
msgstr ""
"**Delete**: delete the product and its data (a confirmation dialog appears)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/home/index.rst:48
msgid "**编辑信息**：修改产品名称及标签（在弹出的编辑窗口中操作）。"
msgstr "**Edit Info**: change the product name and tags (in a pop-up editor)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/home/index.rst:49
msgid "**导出为文件**：将该产品导出为 ``.zip`` 文件，便于备份或迁移到其它机台。"
msgstr ""
"**Export as File**: export the product as a ``.zip`` file for backup or "
"migration to another machine."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/home/index.rst:51
msgid "**批量操作**"
msgstr "**Batch operations**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/home/index.rst:53
msgid "产品表格左侧提供复选框，可多选产品后执行批量操作："
msgstr ""
"The checkboxes on the left of the product table let you select multiple "
"products for batch operations:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/home/index.rst:55
msgid "**删除所选记录**：同时删除多个已选产品。"
msgstr "**Delete selected records**: delete every selected product."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/home/index.rst:56
msgid "**添加标签…**：为所有已选产品批量添加一个标签。"
msgstr "**Add tag…**: add a tag to every selected product."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/home/index.rst:57
msgid "**移除标签…**：从所有已选产品批量移除一个标签。"
msgstr "**Remove tag…**: remove a tag from every selected product."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/home/index.rst:59
msgid "**标签过滤与搜索**"
msgstr "**Tag filter and search**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/home/index.rst:61
msgid "产品列表上方提供两种过滤方式："
msgstr "Above the product list, two filtering controls are available:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/home/index.rst:63
msgid "**按标签筛选** （多选下拉框）：同时选中多个标签时取交集过滤产品列表。"
msgstr ""
"**Filter by tag** (multi-select drop-down): selecting multiple tags filters "
"the list by their intersection."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/home/index.rst:64
msgid "**搜索** （文本输入框）：按产品名称关键字过滤。"
msgstr "**Search** (text input): filter by product-name keyword."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/home/index.rst:66
msgid "**上传 PCBA 文件**"
msgstr "**Upload PCBA file**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/home/index.rst:68
msgid ""
"**上传PCBA文件(.zip)**：点击此按钮选取由\"导出为文件\"生成的 ``.zip`` "
"压缩包，将其导入为新产品；导入完成后产品列表自动刷新。若导入的产品名与系统中已有产品重名，则会提示冲突错误。"
msgstr ""
"**Upload PCBA File (.zip)**: pick a ``.zip`` produced by *Export as File* to"
" import it as a new product; the list refreshes automatically when the "
"import finishes. If the imported product's name collides with an existing "
"one, a conflict error is shown."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/home/index.rst:70
msgid "**磁盘使用情况**"
msgstr "**Disk usage**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/home/index.rst:72
msgid ""
"顶部导航栏右侧（全局可见，非仅限主页）显示 **磁盘使用** 微件，以环形图展示 C: 盘已用与剩余空间比例，悬停可查看具体 GB 数据。当可用空间低于"
" 25% 时显示黄色警告，低于 10% 时显示红色严重警告并闪烁。点击刷新图标可立即重新查询。"
msgstr ""
"The **Disk Usage** widget on the right of the top nav bar (visible on every "
"page, not just Home) shows the used and free C: drive space as a donut "
"chart; hover to see the exact gigabytes. When free space drops below 25% the"
" widget turns yellow; below 10% it turns red and flashes. Click the refresh "
"icon to re-query immediately."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/home/index.rst:-1
msgid "磁盘使用情况微件，显示 C: 容量、警示图标与刷新按钮"
msgstr ""
"Disk-Usage widget showing C: capacity, warning icon, and refresh button."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/home/index.rst:80
msgid "**注意事项**"
msgstr "**Notes**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/home/index.rst:82
msgid "**急停状态下**：新建检测任务、编辑产品等按钮将被禁用，需先点击\"重置轨道\"恢复正常状态。"
msgstr ""
"**Under Emergency Stop**: New Inspection Task, Edit Product, and similar "
"buttons are disabled — click *Reset Track* first."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/home/index.rst:83
msgid "**编辑信息** 对应 UI 标签为\"编辑信息\"，用于修改产品名称和标签；与 **编辑** 不同，后者进入产品的完整编程页面。"
msgstr ""
"**Edit Info** in the UI is labelled *Edit Info* and only changes the product"
" name and tags; **Edit** is different — it opens the full programming page."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/home/index.rst:84
msgid ""
"**训练PCBA** 和产品管理区域仅对 **管理员** 与 **编程员** 角色显示；**操作员** 角色只能看到新建检测任务入口和最近检测任务列表。"
msgstr ""
"**Train PCBA** and the product-management area are visible only to "
"**Administrator** and **Programmer** roles; **Operators** see only the New "
"Inspection Task entry and the Recent inspection tasks list."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/home/index.rst:85
msgid "标签（Tag）在产品行内以小徽章形式显示，可通过\"编辑信息\"对单个产品修改标签，或通过批量操作同时为多个产品添加/移除标签。"
msgstr ""
"Tags appear as small badges on each product row. Edit tags per product via "
"*Edit Info*, or add/remove them in bulk via the batch operations."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/home/index.rst:87
msgid "**相关页面**"
msgstr "**Related pages**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/home/index.rst:89
msgid ":ref:`检测与反馈` — 由\"新建检测任务\"进入"
msgstr ":ref:`检测与反馈` — entered from *New Inspection Task*"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/home/index.rst:90
msgid ":ref:`创建产品` — 由\"训练PCBA\"进入"
msgstr ":ref:`创建产品` — entered from *Train PCBA*"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/home/index.rst:91
msgid ":ref:`查看检测历史（数据分析报告）` — 由\"工作列表\"进入"
msgstr ":ref:`查看检测历史（数据分析报告）` — entered from *Worklist*"

